Detailed Description

Native representation of the trainer's key ball pocket in Generation II.

All items in this list should be contiguous, and the amount should match the value in the count field. If the count value is too small, the game will ignore any later items, and if it is too large, whatever happens to be in memory will be parsed as items, leading to undefined behavior when used.
